        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Nehemiah 12:24",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": " or rather of the king of Persia: ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "p",
        "class": "",
        "text": "that a certain portion should be for the singers, due for every day; he settled a daily salary for them, to be paid out of his treasury; having perhaps a peculiar respect for such sort of men, being a lover of music, by means of which they had a settled habitation in Jerusalem. ",
        "children": [
